'''Dumathoin Thunderstone''' was a Captain of the Guard of [[Thunderholme]], some time before the fall of the city in the {{yearlinkName|1054}}. The [[Dumathoin's bracers|dwarf's bracers]] eventually found their way to [[Aurgloroasa]]'s treasure hoard.
{{Quote
|Hold the gates! No green-skin will step one foot into Thunderholme!
|Dumathoin Thunderstone, Captain of the Guard
}}
